"6  large Cubanelle or green bell peppers (about 1 1/3 pounds)","4  large poblano chiles (about 1 pound)","3  red Fresno chiles","1 tablespoon olive oil, divided","1  (2 1/4-pound) boneless pork shoulder, cut into 3/4-inch pieces","2 cups chopped yellow onion","6  garlic cloves, chopped","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro stems","2 teaspoons chili powder","1 1/2 teaspoons dried oregano","1 teaspoon ground cumin","4 cups unsalted chicken stock (such as Swanson)","2 teaspoons brown sugar","1 1/2 teaspoons kosher salt","4  large tomatillos, finely chopped","3 tablespoons masa harina","1/2 cup light sour cream","1/4 cup fresh cilantro leaves"